{"tid":1234162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔想就咁輸啊","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T06:41:15.000Z","uid":84396,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c889bd3027c742d73ab15b87932f5104466333","tid":1234162,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:32.000Z","msg":"係場夢入面 衝既衝 中煙中彈中胡椒 被捕既被捕 犧牲既犧牲<br />\n<br />\n無錯係換左更多人出黎展示民意 但之後呢？<br />\n<br />\n政府hea覆 語言偽術 一班政棍又出黎當贏左<br />\n然後又再出現抗爭碎片化 步雨傘後塵<br />\n<br />\n警犬又懶係釋出善意 搏傳媒輿論轉向 某程度上又哄返掂一班人<br />\n<br />\n依家和理非有一部份變左袋住先<br />\n勇武派無左目標 難以搵目標再進行下一步行動 爭取實際效果 成個抗爭就好似過左熱戀期漸漸降溫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拖下拖下人民就唔再熱血啦 擺耐左又唔記得晒當初既目的<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講自己好大貢獻好大影響力 但行我又行過晒 衝我又衝過晒 真係唔想見到成件事就咁慢慢冷落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為我地乜都未爭取到啊！</span>"},{"pid":"2abf0446c16f21dd5f8d39532dd59de6a0b60b9d","tid":1234162,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:56:56.000Z","msg":"失敗主義不是無為的理由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234103</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望經過今次大家學識抱打不平，友善照舊，有錯就要屌！<br />\n<br />\n分化輿論要由我地親手阻止<br />\n<br />\n戰場唔止熱門仲有係最新"},{"pid":"ada3c198759af74e58dec910e4c17fc1b74aaba7","tid":1234162,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:57:52.000Z","msg":"每日都搵林鄭啦"},{"pid":"5c7060f79e9a09847cfc01fccaed4f2eade408e9","tid":1234162,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:59:10.000Z","msg":"我路係想散播失敗主義 我深信香港人未輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢刻真係好兩頭唔到岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff33e26c709ba3935a165982950d6bf56c4351a5","tid":1234162,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c7060f79e9a09847cfc01fccaed4f2eade408e9","tid":1234162,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:59:10.000Z","msg":"我路係想散播失敗主義 我深信香港人未輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢刻真係好兩頭唔到岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:59:20.000Z","msg":"唔*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92198589e7955c66ff21112091ac42ff646720f","tid":1234162,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:00:28.000Z","msg":"大家俾啲耐性，等事件發酵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"858e9c568c1624923d8055f2e6c0940cd6dbc354","tid":1234162,"uid":31922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:02:22.000Z","msg":"唯有繼續和平示威"},{"pid":"87db79c9d3687a84fc77c063a43240ee0ed73e13","tid":1234162,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:09:03.000Z","msg":"等於賭錢咁 贏左二百萬 就覺得再賭落去就可以贏埋間賭場返黎 記住莊永遠唔會怕你長賭 賺左二百肯走出賭場門口 以後可以做更多野"},{"pid":"d5869068105f53a453668c23500c54c5c96853f6","tid":1234162,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"唔怕嘅<br />\n<br />\n大家市民付出咗咁多汗水同時間， 應該願意持續監察住呢件事<br />\n<br />\n而且已經有人表示， 如果政府之後又玩嘢， 會願意每個星期都遊行"},{"pid":"289a393fde87de7106e980184936bbdb4fe91535","tid":1234162,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"但係再擲鐵通 同磚<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得冇咩用&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n因為就算義士們沖到入去&ldquo;圓形道場&rdquo; 都唔代表啲咩<br />\n<br />\n只係畀警察有藉口購買多啲裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259f1af8feace66